{"tid":2261685,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"獲德國難民身份反修例示威者稱香港司法敗壞出走","createTime":"2020-10-28T13:39:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T14:27:46.000Z","uid":51271,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2eec201694078b9228ca0aab9238f72b9326ee2d","tid":2261685,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T13:39:24.000Z","msg":"香港司法系統真係dead body<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1557118-20201028.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1557118-20201028.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=wqADD7%2BrbugmZDmBsEVo7LYQZcr3xUkCoBtK5HAxbhw%3D&h=f348c8ba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1557118-20201028.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=b4187c47\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1557118-20201028.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一名香港反修例示威者獲得德國給予難民身分，成為反修例運動爆發以來首位獲得當地政治庇護的香港示威者，她說自己是對香港歸屬感最強的年輕世代，因為香港司法敗壞出走。<br />\n<br />\n23歲事主接受台灣傳媒訪問時說，去年11月中被捕，被控暴動罪和違反「禁蒙面法」，在獲保釋後一星期內決定離開，坐飛機經台灣飛往德國。<br />\n<br />\n她說，抵埗當天就直接到難民接待中心，稱最難適應是語言問題，但營內難民彼此體諒，關係融洽。她等了接近一年，到本月14日收到通知正式獲得難民身分。<br />\n<br />\n她目前住在政府提供的公寓，表示從小到大看香港的變化，也看到律師在中國受到的殘忍對待，對中國沒什麼好感。<br />\n<br />\n特區政府上星期召見德國駐港總領事，抗議德國「假借名義收留罪犯」。外長王毅上月訪問柏林時也強調香港事務是內政，警告外國插手。"},{"pid":"16a6737be2861dafdee87c5ab32b29c4bbee389b","tid":2261685,"uid":231583,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T13:40:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4547d7241c796b44b745f28fa4d1ad6bd0966d6c","tid":2261685,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T14:12:54.000Z","msg":"Agree"},{"pid":"ce9682d22ccda0611fcabc8bd91af06ff9652885","tid":2261685,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16a6737be2861dafdee87c5ab32b29c4bbee389b","tid":2261685,"uid":231583,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime